Stacey Dooley celebrated her 36th birthday and the documentary maker detailed the "greatest gift" she has ever received. The TV presenter shared an adorable photo with her newborn baby Minnie who she cradled in her arms. The on-screen star was dressed casually as she sported a vest top teamed with denim combat trousers and stood barefoot. Stacey kissed her little one's cheek as Minnie rested on her mum's shoulder. She captioned the heartwarming post: "36 [balloon emoji]. The best is yet to come. "T H A N K U EVS SINGLE PERSON THATS WISHED ME A HAPPY BIRTHDAY. "Kev, thank you for the greatest gift of all."(sic)